.SH "CAVEATS"
.P
\fR\fBDifferences from ripgrep:\fR
.P
- \fR\fI--follow\fR is enabled by default for \fR\fIbatgrep\fR.
.P
- Not all the \fR\fIripgrep\fR options are supported.
